channel.title: Problem when trying to connect to a few servers
channel.description: When I try to connect to a few servers, it says " Unexpected server response. Please try using a different world." Why does it say this, and how do i fix it?

item.title: Problem when trying to connect to a few servers
item.dc:creator: @drpibb81 drpibb81
item.description:
@drpibb81 wrote:

Everything was spelled correctly, and it wasnt Hamachi. I could connect to other servers fine, but it wouldnt let me connect to this one.

item.title: Problem when trying to connect to a few servers
item.dc:creator: @teric6 teric6
item.description:
@teric6 wrote:

Make sure you have typed the IP in correct, and haven’t missed a “.” out, also, makes sure your hamachi’s turned on, you’ve joined their network and you firewall is turned off.
